The U.S. would be insane to go it alone on trade and manufacturingPunching down on our allies will not help the middle class. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-us-would-be-insane-to-go-it-alone https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-us-would-be-insane-to-go-it-aloneNoah Smith Fri, 05 Apr 2024 01:06:01 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F73951205-b7b7-429e-b5c4-ad6533882105_1024x1024.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F73951205-b7b7-429e-b5c4-ad6533882105_1024x1024.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F73951205-b7b7-429e-b5c4-ad6533882105_1024x1024.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F73951205-b7b7-429e-b5c4-ad6533882105_1024x1024.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F73951205-b7b7-429e-b5c4-ad6533882105_1024x1024.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F73951205-b7b7-429e-b5c4-ad6533882105_1024x1024.jpeg" width="680" height="680" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/73951205-b7b7-429e-b5c4-ad6533882105_1024x