 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F552e0472-5083-4e2b-a982-cfb046d1dcff_1111x855.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div></blockquote><p>That&#39;s absolutely stunning.印度在 2010 年代成功实现的减贫目标与中国十年前成功实现的目标类似： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png" width="1020" height="732" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/dd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:732,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:103756,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd974e24-fe46-4af3-816d-209b4fee14fe_1020x732.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>自市场自由化以来，印度的国内生产总值增长略落后于中国。但在减贫方面，它正在跟上步伐。</p><p>重要的是，印度成功地减少了这么多贫困，<em>同时也减少了不平等</em>。巴拉和巴辛认为，这是由于印度政府注重对农村地区的再分配：</p><blockquote><p>城乡<em>不平等</em>现象前所未有地减少。城市基尼系数（x100）从36.7下降到31.9；农村基尼系数从28.7下降到27.0。在不平等分析史上，这种下降是闻所未闻的，尤其是在人均高增长的背景下……</p><p>鉴于通过各种公共资助项目大力推动再分配的政策，农村地区相对较高的消费增长不应令人意外。其中包括建设厕所的国家使命，以及确保普遍获得电力、现代烹饪燃料以及最近的自来水的努力。例如，截至 2019 年 8<sup>月</sup>15 日，印度<a href="https://ejalshakti.gov.in/jjmreport/JJMIndia.aspx">农村地区自来水普及率</a>为 16.8%，目前为 74.7%。由于获得安全饮用水而减少的疾病可能有助于家庭赚取更多收入。同样，根据<a href="https://www.niti.gov.in/aspirational-districts-programme">“理想地区计划”</a> ，该国 112 个地区被确定为发展指标最低的地区。这些地区是政府政策的目标，明确注重提高其发展绩效。</p></blockquote><p>回想一下，中国的减贫遵循了一个更典型的模式：经济自由化，富人变得更加富有，速度更快，穷人的生活水平提高，但速度比富人慢，<a href="https://www.aeaweb.org/articles?id=10.1257/aer.20170973">不平等加剧</a>。我们已经习惯于认为不平等加剧是经济快速发展不可避免的代价，但印度的事实证明并非如此。</p><p>也许民主毕竟对发展有用。</p><h4> 2. 美国的朋友和敌人</h4><p>盖洛普发布了<a href="https://news.gallup.com/poll/612170/americans-china-nation-top-foe-russia-second.aspx">一项新的民意调查</a>，询问美国人他们喜欢哪些国家，以及他们认为哪些国家是敌人。头条新闻大多是关于“敌人”的问题，我想这并不奇怪，因为“敌人”是一个强烈而可怕的词。无论如何，有这样的故事：共和党人认为中国是我们最大的敌人，民主党人认为俄罗斯是我们最大的敌人，独立人士普遍同意共和党人的观点，但也比任何一方更有可能认为美国本身是我们自己最大的敌人： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg" width="694" height="384.3817330210773" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:473,&quot;width&quot;:854,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:694,&quot;bytes&quot;:30099,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14386dd5-8323-45f2-903c-169ab734821d_854x473.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption"> Source: <a href="https://news.gallup.com/poll/612170/americans-china-nation-top-foe-russia-second.aspx">Gallup</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>老实说，我必须把它交给这里的独立人士。</p><p>但我也认为美国人（和美国媒体）花太多时间思考谁是国家的<em>敌人</em>，而没有足够的时间思考谁是国家的<em>朋友</em>。考虑我们的敌人会让我们陷入“单打独斗”的心态，这在面对像中国这样比我们强大得多的国家时是致命的。美国是一个中等规模的国家，需要许多盟友才能在《冷战 2》中获胜并阻止热战。</p><p>这意味着我们必须克服孤立主义心态——错误地认为我们两边都有两大洋，可以保护我们免受欧亚大陆冲突的影响。我们必须考虑我们可以与谁合作。因此，很高兴看到盖洛普还询问了美国人他们对哪些国家有好感： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg" width="688" height="636.0141676505312" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:783,&quot;width&quot;:847,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:688,&quot;bytes&quot;:56746,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62a3d9eb-5a8a-4b79-88ca-e64e6ddbf971_847x783.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这是一个好的开始，尽管我希望民意调查机构询问美国人对印度尼西亚、波兰、越南、土耳其和巴基斯坦的看法。令我惊喜的是，很少有受访者对这些国家“没有意见”，所以我认为这里还有补充的空间。</p><p>无论如何，我们可以看到美国人倾向于喜欢民主国家，不喜欢专制国家。对欧洲国家没有明显的偏见，因为俄罗斯排名垫底，而英国、法国和德国排名接近顶部。人们可能对中东国家有一点不喜欢，这有望促使美国人重新将我们的资源从该地区撤走。</p><p> Most interestingly, most well liked country, as measured by the difference between favorable and unfavorable, is Japan.美国人<em>真的非常非常</em>喜欢日本。正如他们应该的那样！首先，这意味着那些试图通过提出针对日本的保护主义担忧来迎合的美国政客—— <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/us-steel-falls-on-report-biden-will-voice-concern-on-nippon-deal?sref=R8NfLgwS">拜登反对</a>新日铁收购美国钢铁公司，或者特朗普对日本钢铁征收关税——可能是找错了对象。其次，这意味着我们媒体或许应该更多地谈论日本<a href="https://scholars-stage.org/losing-taiwan-means-losing-japan/">在台湾的关键安全利益</a>。</p><p>不管怎样，很高兴看到美国人对印度、台湾和韩国表现出压倒性的积极态度。我们的领导人应该更加努力地利用这种积极情绪，推动与这些国家更密切的经济合作。</p><h4> 3. 加拿大怎么了？</h4><p>近几个月来，许多人对加拿大的经济感到担忧。 The country&#39;s real per capita GDP — the most common measure of living standards — has been falling for over a year now: </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg" width="1050" height="700" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:700,&quot;width&quot;:1050,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:64617,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9e6310f4-9b78-4a80-a8ef-b943913f9484_1050x700.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/mikalskuterud/status/1763207065135464872">米卡尔·斯库特鲁德</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>在彭博社最近的一篇专栏文章中，泰勒·考恩<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-03-12/oh-canada-your-economy-is-better-than-you-think?utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;cmpid%3D=socialflow-twitter-view&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_content=view&amp;sref=R8NfLgwS">告诉我们不要担心</a>——加拿大的 GDP 及其中位收入仍在增长。但说实话，他的数据并没有说服力。首先，他贴的图表是GDP<em>总量</em>，而不是人均GDP： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg" width="688" height="417.8067754077792" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:484,&quot;width&quot;:797,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:688,&quot;bytes&quot;:36083,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9d996a0-0ad5-4c3f-b5e0-da15359d44e9_797x484.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-03-12/oh-canada-your-economy-is-better-than-you-think?utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;cmpid%3D=socialflow-twitter-view&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_content=view&amp;sref=R8NfLgwS">泰勒·科恩（Tyler Cowen）</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>你可以看到过去两年令人担忧的扁平化。但那些年，加拿大的人口<em><a href="https://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/canada-population">持续增长！</a></em>所以人均生活水平正在下降！</p><p>泰勒还发布了加拿大收入中位数上升的图表。但他的图表结束于 2021 年——当前增长放缓开始之前！所以这也不太让人放心。</p><p>泰勒指出，实际人均 GDP 是使用 GDP 平减指数而不是消费者价格来根据通货膨胀进行调整的。他将我们链接到<a href="https://twitter.com/stephenfgordon/status/1764439558001721715">加拿大经济学家史蒂芬·戈登 (Stephen Gordon) 的帖子</a>，他认为加拿大在海外销售的商品价格不如加拿大人购买的商品价格重要，因此我们应该看看按消费价格缩减的实际人均 GDP索引代替。</p><p> And yet when Gordon performs this calculation, the results look even more worrying!加拿大扣除CPI后的实际人均GDP在过去两年绝对暴跌，现在仅比十年前高一点！ </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg" width="678" height="533.9490084985836" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2f503150-b5a5-4012-848e-eae2fda660c6_1059x834.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;